metadata.description: **APΞvine** - the genesis collection of Decentrawine. Behind each APΞvine is a real vine with never seen before real-world utilities. Get access to an ecosystem around NFTs and everyone’s favorite: wine! We are building a unicorn DAO vineyard starting with a free mint of our APΞvines. We drop real, big and 1:1 collectible wine bottles as NFTs, a PFP collection, our own token, a Learn2Earn game and much more. Curious? [www.decentrawine.com](https://www.decentrawine.com)
